<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      activeIndex: '1',
      activeIndex2: '1'
    };
  },
  methods: {
    handleSelect(key, keyPath) {
      console.log(key, keyPath);
      if (key == '1-1') {
        this.$router.push({ path: '/user/userinfo' });
      } else if (key == '1-2') {
        this.$router.push({ path: '/user/edituserinfo' });
      } else if (key == '2') {
        this.$router.push({ path: '/user/map' });
      } else if (key == '3') {
        this.$router.push({ path: '/user/device' });
      } else if (key == '4') {
        this.$router.push({ path: '/user/data' });
      }
    }
  }

}
</script>
